   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,231:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     │ /login     │──────────▶  Generates Google OAuth URL              
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,238:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     │ route      │             (includes Client ID + scope + state)    
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,241:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 
