   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,261:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:          │  3. Redirect to Google                                    
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,264:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,272:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:          ▼                                                           
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,274:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
