   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,844:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 11. Security Considerations
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,847:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: This project was designed with security as a top priority:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,849:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Security Measure | Implementation |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,851:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,852:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |---|---|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,854:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,857:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,860:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: No password storage
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,864:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | OAuth 2.0 ensures the app never sees user
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,866:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: passwords |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,869:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,871:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Read-only scope
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,877:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Only 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,879:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: gmail.readonly
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,881:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — cannot send, delete, or modify emails |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,882:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,884:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,887:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Environment
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,889:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: variables
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,893:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | All secrets (Client ID, Secret, Flask Key) stored as env vars, never in code |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,897:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,898:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,900:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: HTTPS enforcement
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,902:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,905:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ProxyFix
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,907:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  middleware ensures secure HTTPS behind Render
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,910:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,912:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s load balancer |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,913:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,915:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,918:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: CSRF protection
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,919:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | OAuth 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,921:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: state
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,931:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,936:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: parameter prevents Cross-Site Request Forgery attacks |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,938:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,939:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,942:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Session encryption
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,948:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Flask sessions are cryptographically
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,950:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: signed with a secret key |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,952:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,954:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,956:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: No database
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,961:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | No persistent storage of user data; everything lives in the session cookie |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,964:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,967:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,971:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Token expiry
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,977:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Access tokens automatically expire; the app handles re-authentication |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,984:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 12. Deployment Architecture
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,990:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The application is deployed using a fully automated CI/CD pipeline:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-18 06:16:34,994:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
